Discovering directory
    pwd

Discovering Archives
    ls -l(more details) -a(all archives)

Creating Archives
    echo "Bem Vindo" > bemvindo.txt

Reading Archive
    cat bemvindo.txt

Manual from commands
    man cat

Adding Lines
    echo "Bem Vindo" >> bemvindo.txt

Creating Directory
    mkdir

Removing Directory
    rmdir (only empty directories)
    rm -r(recursive)

Caracter Coringa
    ? 
    * > all

Copying Files
    cp "name" "name new file"

Moving Files
    mv "name" "name new"

Zipping with tar
    tar -cz "archive" > "new name".tar.gz
    tar -czf "newname".tar.gz
    (accept -v(verbose))

Unzipping with tar
    tar -xz < "archive".tar.gz
    tar -xzf "archive".tar.gz
    (accept -v(verbose))

USING VI 
    Press I to insert some changes
    
    Press X to delete some caracters

    
